**29-9-2025  Monday**
## **Day 3 Git & GitHub Practice Tasks**

1. Resolve a merge conflict between two branches.
2. Stash uncommitted changes and apply them later.
3. Create an annotated Git tag for a commit.
4. View all tags in a repository.
5. Revert a specific commit.
6. Squash multiple commits into one.
7. Set a remote repository URL or change it.
8. Fetch changes from remote without merging.
9. Compare two branches to see differences.
10. Clone a repository and check out a specific branch.

**Solution***

1. git merge branch_name
   git add conflicted_file
   git commit -m "Resolved merge conflict"
2. git stash
   git stash apply
3. git tag -a v1.0 -m "version v1.01 release"
4. git tag
5. git revert commit_hash
6. git rebase -i HEAD~3
7. git remote set-url origin https://github.com/user/repo.git
8. git fetch origin
9. git diff branch1 branch2
10. git clone -b branch_name https://github.com/user/repo.git